rare electrically-charged luminescent crystals

00:04:11.469 --> 00:04:20.050
formed in the ionization of ground radon.
Obviously. But then, a 30,000kph crystal?

00:04:20.050 --> 00:04:25.919
Erling doesn't know what they are, no-one
does. But he knows they aren't a hoax.

00:04:25.919 --> 00:04:34.919
"Several sightings can be explained of course
if you've got this light high up in the sky.

00:04:34.919 --> 00:04:43.319
It has been photographed, it has been recorded
on videotapes and so there is no doubt that

00:04:43.319 --> 00:04:53.180
there is something going on up there. If someone
at this location could put up some instruments

00:04:53.180 --> 00:05:04.000
to see if we've got the same readings as we
do, or other readings also of course, I think

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:07.259
it's very important to get data."

